data.description: Situated on the highly desired West Shore Drive is this 4 bedroom 3 bath well-appointed Crosslake home that boasts a high pride of ownership, charming curb appeal, and a stunning 1.66-acre wooded lot. Main floor of this home features one-level living, gorgeous kitchen with stainless appliances, living room with fireplace, primary bedroom suite and a full laundry room. Finished walk-out lower level has an oversized family room, additional bedrooms, bathroom, dry storage room and utility room. Attached 3 stall heated garage and storage shed offer ample storage options. Sit back and relax with a cold drink on the front porch or share a meal with friends on the back deck that overlooks the private backyard. You will love the great location as it is minutes from all the Crosslake amenities and the trails for hiking or biking. Launch your boat at the Cross Lake public access that is just a half mile down the road and cruise the Whitefish Chain. Don’t miss out on this one!
